{"tid":1698733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術]如何防止敵人衝刺制服手足? 首先執起地下支竹","createTime":"2019-11-07T16:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T19:13:40.000Z","uid":61831,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b547a4e6f79c1ca7ade18639febb93562a75ef","tid":1698733,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:49:33.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過點解一隊哥布林，得幾十隻，都夠膽衝向幾百人，甚至幾千人?<br />\n<br />\n因為<strong>你有頭盔雨傘擋子彈，你有眼罩豬嘴擋毒煙，<span style=\"color: red;\">但係你冇武器擋衝鋒</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n竹作為隨街可見，而且經常大量出現既長條狀物件，絕對係最佳既防衝刺兵器<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以後示威現場見到竹堆，一定要盡可能每人拎起一支竹，只要形成到長竹陣形，敵方既衝鋒就會失效，直接將被制服人數降至零</span><br />\n<br />\n太長導致難以手持既竹則可以作為路障中既拒馬，面向行車路線，強行撞擊將導致車毀人亡，結界師們可以考慮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GQYy07A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGQYy07A.jpg&h=46ffe6a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca97ddbad85c9086771adcca7650beb06de7a4ed","tid":1698733,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:50:03.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"a7a772bdd5ae59ef0ed0e12f6276c468a9b40b10","tid":1698733,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:50:13.000Z","msg":"習曱甴"},{"pid":"784a9ebe2e7c507cc53a8ea1930c23dbb4d8ccc7","tid":1698733,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:50:23.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"358b7538204c54186ce50e3dc9d43ba4b68b1568","tid":1698733,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:50:35.000Z","msg":"習曱甴"},{"pid":"4d7f3f9c8f7cdfd7f2ba8919dca3418918617396","tid":1698733,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:55:46.000Z","msg":"小心，削尖拮親人，所以見到啲竹先萬勿碰，最好放入垃圾收集站由清潔工友處理"},{"pid":"98c724a2b6e331477c2feecda7bd313d9c0e2cb2","tid":1698733,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:56:32.000Z","msg":"推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\